{"tid":2434891,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"點解SQQQ有45%嘅holdings都用黎買美國公債，債價仲不斷跌","createTime":"2021-03-05T21:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T14:47:45.000Z","uid":254330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3f08901b2910240509290bdffa01f7d68efd2fbb","tid":2434891,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T21:44:59.000Z","msg":"question 望高人解答<br />\n$SQQQ 嘅NQ_F淡倉得150張（MAR NQ -150) + 一堆同銀行簽訂嘅納指指數掉期 （佔大約55%）呢堆就屬於NQ嘅short position<br />\n<br />\n其餘大約45%就全部都係US treasury bill, 咁唔洗大家都知道最近treasury bill同其他bonds嘅價格都不斷下降（相對dividend yield不斷上升）, 而$SQQQ就有45% holdings屬於呢堆最近不斷下跌嘅treasury bill ,咁呢堆holdings咪會不斷拖低$SQQQ回報？<br />\n<br />\n根據發行商自己出嘅report 其實好多日跌市嘅回報都不足3x，會唔會係比treasury bill拖累？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a6tkObh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa6tkObh.png&h=d4fe059d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"507ac1ed83ae6c95913c6ca6963d35dab298b17f","tid":2434891,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T21:46:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.proshares.com/funds/sqqq_daily_holdings.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.proshares.com%2Ffunds%2Fsqqq_daily_holdings.html&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedSNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=593ae467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.proshares.com/funds/sqqq_daily_holdings.html</a><br />\nProShares UltraPro Short QQQ Holdings"},{"pid":"a1603b5d041ae4ba392ce092815e16f7a7c9a76e","tid":2434891,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T21:52:05.000Z","msg":"VX相關嘅ETF 無論是否反向/正向 都直接100%用期貨作為holdings 點解又可以全部都透過VX期黎整ETF呢"},{"pid":"060a547e060139f6991c47b51ebfa6c4da037b9e","tid":2434891,"uid":301911,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T00:32:46.000Z","msg":"唔肯定啱唔啱<br />\n但你見佢買既全部都係近債、今年到期果啲<br />\n而近債其實個價跌得好少<br />\n咁多個月波幅都冇0.5%，所以影響唔大<br />\n佢主要都係 short納期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aDiwVMM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaDiwVMM.png&h=0f68fd2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7f1ce191773de56a2019a7d18ccb7276c12ca64","tid":2434891,"uid":301911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T00:33:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p679Hsy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp679Hsy.png&h=a11aa59c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6f872d2ab6df145ce15ffe844c6b91c203d1338","tid":2434891,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:36:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae1078239e70fdc85c99ad724bf1c82cdd405c20","tid":2434891,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T10:38:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa83b0c5d46d1309f3bf2972447efd25ea2064f1","tid":2434891,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T11:31:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22c28af01b3c4deb13d1131f8fa463df03a22dbc","tid":2434891,"uid":355595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T11:38:35.000Z","msg":"T-bill 會hold到到期所以YTM不變,除非要套現比margin"},{"pid":"6e2cf82af1a1fd44f50ab7a1fda1225021572b09","tid":2434891,"uid":352160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T11:49:56.000Z","msg":"short term treasury係risk free<br />\n應該係多出黎既現金食盡埋姐"},{"pid":"4c711938a6c11a42ef3eff8cc4d1a8ef9ff5d746","tid":2434891,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T12:06:36.000Z","msg":"銀行狂做空"},{"pid":"a28deebedae04c99d3c1f9d1af725de5ae8e02fe","tid":2434891,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T14:47:45.000Z","msg":"推"}]}